EX NO 1 : C PROGRAM TO CHECK ElIGIBILITY FOR MARRIAGE (AGE >=21).
DATE:28-04-2025


AIM:
To write a program to check eligibility for marriage using simple if statement.

ALGORITHM:
1. Start.
2. Declare a variable value of type char.
3. Prompt the user to enter a value.
4. Read the value using scanf.
5. Check eligible for marriage.
6. If age >= 21, print "Eligible".
7. If false, print " Not Eligible".
8. End.

PROGRAM:
#include <stdio.h>

int main() 
{
    int age;

    printf("Enter your age: ");
    scanf("%d", &age);

    if (age >= 21) {
        printf("You are eligible for marriage.\n");
    }

    if (age < 21) {
        printf("You are not eligible for marriage.\n");
    }

    return 0;
}

Program to check eligibility for marriage using simple if statement.
